cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DC 

This paper is primarily focused on the application of deep reinforcement learning (DRL) to address the resource allocation problem in federated learning networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also deals with network resource allocation, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of DRL also suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
